            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Iudicio principali <expan><abbr>d<am>dd</am></abbr><ex>ominorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>nn</am></abbr><ex>ostrorum</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">Valentiniani</supplied> <lb n="2"/>Valentis et Gratiani principum <supplied reason="lost">maximorum</supplied> <lb n="3"/>dispositionem <note>sic</note> etiam inlustris viri <supplied reason="lost">utriusque</supplied> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">mi</supplied>litiae magistri Equiti comitis Fo<supplied reason="lost">scanus</supplied> <lb n="5"/>p<expan><ex>rae</ex><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ositus</ex></expan> legionis primae Martiorum u<supplied reason="lost">na cu</supplied>m <lb n="6"/>militibus sibi creditis hunc bu<supplied reason="lost">r</supplied>gum <lb n="7"/>a fondamentis <note>sic</note> et construxit et ad sum<expan><ex>m</ex><abbr>am</abbr></expan> <lb n="8"/>manum operis consulatus Modesti et <lb n="9"/>Arenthei <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>vv</abbr><ex>irorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>cc</abbr><ex>larissimorum</ex></expan> fecit pervenire
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>11 aneinanderpassende Fragmente erhalten. (B): RIU: Z. 8/9: Zeilenfall fehlt.</p>
            </div>
